Amsterdam Ave., east side, north from and including West 75th., to, but not including West 76th Streets. Also shown is West 75th Street, north side, east from Amsterdam, to, but not including Columbus Aves. Prominent building shown at the N.E. corner, is No. 161 West 75th Street.

About 1928.

Knickerbocker Photo Service.

West 75th Street, west from but not including Amsterdam Ave. Intersection shown in the foreground is Broadway.

July 27, 1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
